	(61, 1, '2017-02-20 17:20:13', '2017-02-20 17:20:13', '<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-47" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pexels-photo-59599-1024x681.jpeg" alt="" width="1024" height="681" />Goa has multiple sides to it. There\'s one part that lets you relax and rejuvenate in tranquility, another side that lets you let your hair down and party hard and yet another that lets you to engage in adrenaline-pumping activities like para-sailing and trekking. Goa has something for everyone, which makes it one of the most preferred holiday destinations for the young and old equally. The very air in Goa brings with it calm and will relieve your senses. If you are someone who desires to try their hands a few adventure activities, then Goa is the perfect destination to start. Reserve one of the lovely hotels in Goa or check out the beach cottages for an exciting Goa trip.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">Here are the 5 best local experience\'s in Goa and start planning your trip now!</h1>\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;"><strong>1) Trekking </strong></h1>\r\n[caption id="attachment_5" align="aligncenter" width="550"]<img class="size-full wp-image-5" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/img-20161103-154905-largejpg.jpg" alt="" width="550" height="309" /> Trekking along the coast-side of Arambol[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Goa has several hiking trails for the trekking lovers. The most famous journey is the Dudhsagar travel and the trail that everyone recommends starts from Devil\'s Canyon. Another trek starts near Collem Train station and leads you through dense forests and tricky routes to your destination. A trek to Vagheri Peaks is also quite popular and you will probably be amazed with the abundant nature and trees all around you. The <a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=203">Arambol</a> and <a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=204">Neuti</a> treks are pathways over beautiful coastline will surely be a bliss. <a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=204">You can checkout some exciting treks at unbelievable prices</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">2) <a href="http://spontieapp.com/new_blog/2017/02/16/5-insider-adventures-to-experience-in-goa/">Para-sailing</a></h1>\r\n[caption id="attachment_22" align="aligncenter" width="2500"]<img class="size-full wp-image-22" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/maxresdefault.jpg" alt="" width="2500" height="1406" /> Exciting Parasailing[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">For the water sports activities enthusiasts, Goa is truly a dream come true. Even though the different water sports here aren\'t really of the hard-core variety, they will still give you a chance to get your hang of it. Para-sailing in Goa is one of the most popular water sports activities which can be experienced at seashores like<a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=186"> Baga, Vagator, Palolem, Calangute and Miramar.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">3) <a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=187">Jet Skiing</a></h1>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-10" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/rincon-jet-ski.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="540" />\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Water skiing is another water sport that will definitely get the adrenaline rushing. If you have the need for speed then you definitely have to try riding a jet ski during your holiday in Goa. Jet skiing is one of the most exciting and thrilling water sports activities being offered in Goa. It is perfect for those vacationers and tourists seeking adventure as well as those who want to just have a fun experience with family and friends. Although it appears dangerous and hard to master, water skiing courses at Goa will ensure you learn the ropes of it before you make the leap! <a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/experience.php?id=187">Book jet ski in Goa at amazing prices Now!</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">4) Wild Life Safari</h1>\r\n[caption id="attachment_11" align="aligncenter" width="2144"]<img class="size-full wp-image-11" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/ec26cfdca37c8e892834f5ed4f3ce668.jpg" alt="" width="2144" height="1424" /> Wild Life Safari[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Goa, being situated in the very run of nature, is home to a few wild animals sanctuaries and national theme parks that you can visit for your fix of adrenaline. Nature and pet lovers will love these places in Goa! A few of these sanctuaries include Cotigao Wildlife Sanctuary, Mollem National Park, Salim Ali Bird Sanctuary and Mahavir Wildlife Sanctuary. You can take in the picturesque views and revel in a safari while discovering Goa\'s bountiful nature.<a href="http://spontieapp.com/mobile/Goa.php"> Discover and book amazing things to do in Goa at unbeatable prices.</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h1 style="text-align: center;">5) Go Karting</h1>\r\n[caption id="attachment_12" align="aligncenter" width="1920"]<img class="size-full wp-image-12" src="http://spontieapp.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/runway-9-hyderabad.jpg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" /> Go-Karting in Goa[/caption]\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">If you have a need for acceleration, then Go Karting at Goa is a must-do! This high-speed racing sport affords a much-needed excitement to adventure lovers. You will find two of the country\'s best Proceed Karting tracks in Goa, one at Nuvem town and the other one at Arpora. Race along the winding tracks and compete with your friends in this sport of high-speed racing!</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">Besides these adventure activities, there are tons of sites in Goa. Goa is a hub for tourists from across the world and it sees visitors through the year. Enjoy your Goa vacation without having to worry about accommodation by booking one of the classy hotels in Goa in the start. Which other activity do you add to this set of the 5 best experience in Goa?</p>', '5 Insider adventures to experience in Goa', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '28-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-20 17:20:13', '2017-02-20 17:20:13', '', 28, 'http://spontieapp.com/blog/2017/02/20/28-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
